{"tid":478960,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"【Orage台】你的瞄準真可笑  Day152 24/11","createTime":"2017-11-24T14:45:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-24T17:12:20.000Z","uid":122942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"da32709a8766371de2a263eecf7121fdfaf2242b","tid":478960,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T14:45:40.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/5ADqP2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F5ADqP2.gif&h=8c5a58f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家好，我係Orage。 我會於每晚11點至2點開台玩遊戲同與觀眾聊天。<br />\n因為我極度3分鐘熱度，所以好少會一直玩同一隻Game。<br />\n有興趣嘅巴打入黎捧下場，一齊傾下計啦  <br />\n<br />\n今晚11點左右見 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Foragejan%20&d=1jv8LJm6VaFhRmhi9skO%2Br%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=04cc1058\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan </a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/W4CK8P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FW4CK8P.png&h=69cccb5f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外我開左個FB專頁，有時會PO日常野同覺得有趣嘅事，<br />\n希望巴打們可以入黎比個讚。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oragejan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foragejan&d=1jv8LJm6VaFhRmhi9skO%2Br%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=bf577aaf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oragejan</a></div>"},{"pid":"da741475ad44a067f4580c4a3c4c2cd99de92176","tid":478960,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T14:58:04.000Z","msg":"已開[run]"},{"pid":"dc627919ebe6a50dc42e9af2ecd1ae9d03163b5f","tid":478960,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-24T14:59:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca752e024571b837ea53e8ea65cf371688434738","tid":478960,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r